sequenceDiagram
    actor "Client Contact" as ClientContact
    participant "Presentation.Frontend.SPA" as PresentationFrontendSPA
    participant "Application.API.Host" as ApplicationAPIHost
    participant "Project Management Service" as ProjectManagementService
    participant "Security Infrastructure" as SecurityInfrastructure
    participant "Persistence Infrastructure" as PersistenceInfrastructure
    participant "Audit Service" as AuditService
    participant "Notification Service" as NotificationService

    ClientContact->>PresentationFrontendSPA: 1. 1. Clicks secure link in email (e.g., https://app.emp.com/approve/milestone/{token})
    PresentationFrontendSPA-->>ClientContact: Page load request
    activate ApplicationAPIHost
    PresentationFrontendSPA->>ApplicationAPIHost: 2. 2. Requests milestone details for review
    ApplicationAPIHost-->>PresentationFrontendSPA: 200 OK with MilestoneReviewDto | 4xx Error
    ApplicationAPIHost->>SecurityInfrastructure: 3. 3. ValidateApprovalToken(token)
    SecurityInfrastructure-->>ApplicationAPIHost: TokenValidationResult (Success/FailureReason)
    activate ProjectManagementService
    ApplicationAPIHost->>ProjectManagementService: 4. 4. GetMilestoneForReview(tokenPayload)
    ProjectManagementService-->>ApplicationAPIHost: MilestoneReviewDto
    ProjectManagementService->>PersistenceInfrastructure: 4.1. 4.1. FindAsync(milestoneId)
    PersistenceInfrastructure-->>ProjectManagementService: Milestone entity with Project navigation property
    ClientContact->>PresentationFrontendSPA: 5. 5. Reviews details and clicks 'Approve'
    PresentationFrontendSPA-->>ClientContact: POST request submission
    PresentationFrontendSPA->>ApplicationAPIHost: 6. 6. Submits milestone approval
    ApplicationAPIHost-->>PresentationFrontendSPA: 200 OK | 4xx Error
    ApplicationAPIHost->>ProjectManagementService: 7. 7. ApproveMilestone(command)
    ProjectManagementService->>SecurityInfrastructure: 7.1. 7.1. ValidateApprovalToken(token)
    SecurityInfrastructure-->>ProjectManagementService: TokenValidationResult
    ProjectManagementService->>PersistenceInfrastructure: 7.2. 7.2. BeginTransaction()
    PersistenceInfrastructure-->>ProjectManagementService: Transaction object
    ProjectManagementService->>PersistenceInfrastructure: 7.3. 7.3. Update milestone status to 'Approved' and invalidate token
    ProjectManagementService->>AuditService: 7.4. 7.4. LogEvent(auditEntry)
    ProjectManagementService->>PersistenceInfrastructure: 7.5. 7.5. CommitTransaction()
    activate NotificationService
    ProjectManagementService->>NotificationService: 8. 8. (Post-Commit) Raise Domain Event: MilestoneApprovedEvent
    NotificationService->>NotificationService: 8.1. 8.1. Send milestone approval notification to System Admin
    ApplicationAPIHost->>PresentationFrontendSPA: 9. 9. Returns 200 OK success response
    PresentationFrontendSPA-->>ApplicationAPIHost: HTTP/1.1 200 OK
    PresentationFrontendSPA->>ClientContact: 10. 10. Displays success confirmation message: 'Thank you! The milestone has been approved.'

    note over SecurityInfrastructure: **Error Handling: Expired/Used Token** During step 3, if the Security Infrastructure determines t...
    note over ApplicationAPIHost: **Idempotency** The API endpoint for approval (Step 6) must be idempotent. The second token valid...

    deactivate NotificationService
    deactivate ProjectManagementService
    deactivate ApplicationAPIHost
